  (gr_text "---
PCB LAYOUT NOTES (do not place components in these areas):
- Buck inductor (L1): 10mm radius keep-out on top layer (no analog traces)
- Crystal (X1): 5mm radius keep-out all layers
- MCU center at (80,55) — route all signals radially outward
- Power traces: 0.5mm min width for 5V/3.3V, 1.5mm for VBAT
- CAN: 120ohm diff pair, 0.25mm width, 0.25mm gap
- USB: 90ohm diff pair, 0.3mm width, 0.2mm gap
- Solder mask: green LPI
- Copper finish: ENIG
- All mounting holes: M4 screw, 4.5mm drill, 8mm copper pad
---" (at 5 0 0) (layer "Cmts.User") (effects (font (size 1 1))))
